  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was released from my position in the tanneries, working for the Red Army, as I mentioned that my boss was not-- was the minister to light-- from light-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the light industry, Mr.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They arranged for me there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a truck where my-- that I and my wife, some of my belongings-- even a piano that I got up-- got back-- find out who the piano was taken away by a Lithuanian when the Russian came in.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was loaded on the truck, and the truck from the army was bringing me to Bialystock.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I know also that Lublin was liberated through the-- from the-- of the Germans, liberated through the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when I came to Bialystock, I ask that governor, Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], to allow me to go to Lublin, because Lublin wasn't far from Radom, and I'm very anxious to find out what happens to my father and my family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I promise him I didn't-- that I would come back to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Came to Lublin, and so I went to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In Lublin, the government [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] find out that I am there, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I told them about this, that I have to go back to Bialystock.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Radom wasn't yet liberated-- that I would have to go back to Bialystock because I promise that [INAUDIBLE] that I am coming, that-- They said, no, you are not going back there, because we need you [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] in Gdansk, in Danzig, where there was some tanneries there, and that you would have to put in motion the tanneries over there, and we are sending you over there.",
      "word_count": 70
    }
  ],
